(1. Introduction) Tj
0 -14 Td
(AYRA ERP is a web-based academic enterprise resource planning system for students, teachers,) Tj
0 -14 Td
(academic office staff, and communication teams. It manages student records, subjects, classes,) Tj
0 -14 Td
(advisories, leave requests, approvals, calendar events, and email alerts.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
