0 -14 Td
(- Student: profile, progress, classes, advisories, calendar, leave requests, photo upload) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Teacher: student management, subjects, classes, advisories, progress, leave approval, alerts) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Academic Office: teachers, curriculum, timetables, approvals, records, leave monitor, alerts) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Communication: announcements, campaigns, events, response tracking) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(3. Alert System) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Email alerts use Nodemailer with Gmail app password configuration) Tj
0 -14 Td
